---
title: Rich Bacon, Leek & Greens Fusilli with Capsicum Relish Sauce & Parmesan Cheese
description: You can add just about anything to a pasta, an entire veggie garden can be chopped up and tossed through a rich sauce.
Sometimes, simple really is best though. Leek, capsicum relish and some greens in a creamy tomato sauce is all this dish needs to leave you feeling full and oh-so happy.
